725561f-b.title: Queens: 66th Avenue - Alderton Street
725561f-b.text:
~Sixty-sixth Avenue (WRite Pot Road) north side, in line
of Alderton Street, showing in three views the Springsteen
house. Michael S. Srpingsteen (b.1804 d. 1886) erected this
house in 1859. His son Dueid who married Anna W. Monfort of
Brooklyn inherited it. He died ahout 1912. His widow sold
it in 1928.
May 1923
View 2: April 1923
View 3: July 1923
Eumene L. Armhruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
